Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 前奏
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(眾小馬)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:35.31,Ponyvillans,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}小馬鎮，致 Pinkie Pie...\NPonyville to Pinkie Pie...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.48,0:00:42.12,Ponyvillans,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}小馬鎮，致 Pinkie Pie...\NPonyville to Pinkie Pie...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.46,0:00:50.90,Ponyvillans,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}你突然不見，我們都不知為何\NSeems you've left us, and we're all still wond'ring why
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:56.30,Ponyvillans,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}小馬鎮，致 Pinkie Pie...\NPonyville to Pinkie Pie...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:03.28,Ponyvillans,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}我們還愛你，別躲起來\NWe still love you, don't you hide
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.51,0:01:13.25,Ponyvillans,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}如你聽得見，你應該知道怎麼辦...\NIf this reaches you, you'll know just what to do...
Comment: 0,0:01:23.46,0:01:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-1
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(眾小馬)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.26,0:01:27.80,Ponyvillans,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}這裡是小馬鎮，致 Pinkie Pie\NThis is Ponyville to Pinkie Pie
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.07,0:01:31.37,Ponyvillans,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}只是想要跟你說\Njust wanted you to know
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.77,0:01:38.48,Ponyvillans,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們想你，我們只希望你回家\Nthat we miss you, and we wish that you were home
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.08,0:01:45.92,Ponyvillans,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但我們也沒有權力說你的去處\Nbut it's not our place to say where you should go
Comment: 0,0:01:47.65,0:01:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-2
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(Pinkie)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.65,0:01:52.29,Pinkie,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}看來我一直對自己撒謊\NSeems that I've been lying to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.69,0:01:56.36,Pinkie,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}從未如此困難\Nit's never been so hard
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.50,0:02:03.54,Pinkie,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我的蹄子好像帶我走太過\Nand I think my hooves have taken me too far
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.40,0:02:10.78,Pinkie,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我想我該停下，聽聽我的想法\NGuess it's time I stopped and listened to my heart
Comment: 0,0:02:11.74,0:02:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,## 橋段
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(兩邊)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.74,0:02:18.98,Both,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,2000)}但是，看來我們已陷入了僵局\NBut here are we sitting at an impasse
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:25.99,Both,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,2000)}困在這月球\NTrapped on the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:35.13,Both,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,2000)}火箭已飛走，我們已不在家鄉\NRocketship is gone and I'm not where I belong
