Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(Pinkie)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:07.80,Pinkie,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}雖然我試著說服自己\NThough I've tried convincing otherwise
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:12.17,Pinkie,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我感到好孤獨\NI'm feeling so alone
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.70,0:03:18.68,Pinkie,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}什麼事都看著好陰沉灰暗\NThings aren't looking on the bright side anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.75,0:03:22.91,Pinkie,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}要是我有路回家——\NIf I just had some way home--
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(眾小馬)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:26.08,Ponyvillans,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}——我們帶你走\N--we'll take you there
