Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.59,0:03:31.06,Ponyvillans,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}Pinkie Pie, 正是時刻\NPinkie Pie, the time has come
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:34.29,Ponyvillans,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}還來得及，你就上來\NIt's not too late, so just hop on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:37.20,Ponyvillans,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}準備好沒，Pinkie Pie?\NAre you ready, Pinkie Pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:40.63,Ponyvillans,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}要不要跟，Pinkie Pie?\NAre you with us, Pinkie Pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.17,0:03:44.10,Ponyvillans,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}聽得見嗎, Pinkie Pie?\NCan you hear us, Pinkie Pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:45.24,Ponyvillans,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}聽得——\NCan you--
